            <title><![CDATA[Neverness to Everness opening animation ‘Hypervortex Before the Storm’]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/neverness-to-everness-opening-animation-hypervortex-before-the-storm</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/neverness-to-everness-opening-animation-%E2%80%98hypervortex-before-the-storm%E2%80%99.1227621/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/mobile/smartphone">Smartphone</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Closed beta test begins July 3.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Perfect World Games [25 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/perfect-world-games">Perfect World Games</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Hotta Studio [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/perfect-world-games/hotta-studio">Hotta Studio</a> have released the opening animation for <em><a title="Games > Neverness to Everness [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/neverness-to-everness">Neverness to Everness</a></em> ahead of the <a title="Genres > Free-to-Play [404 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/free-to-play">free-to-play</a> supernatural urban <a title="Genres > Open-World [664 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/open-world">open-world</a> <a title="Genres > RPG [17,389 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a>‘s closed “Containment Test,” which <a href="https://nte.perfectworld.com/en/article/news/gamenews/20250610/256772.html" target="_blank">will run</a> from July 3 to 16 on <a title="Platforms > PC [23,577 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>. <span id="more-975856"></span></p><p><em>Neverness to Everness</em> will be available for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,807 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, PC, iOS, and Android. A release date has yet to be announced.</p><p>Watch the opening animation below.</p><h2><span>Opening Animation: Hypervortex Before the Storm</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="NTE Opening Animation | Hypervortex Before the Storm" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6M7b_00KDgk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="NTEオープニング映像丨「スパイラ」、嵐の一歩前に" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6pBY7HSM_Oc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/neverness-to-everness-opening-animation-hypervortex-before-the-storm]]></content:encoded>
