            <title><![CDATA[Everybody’s Golf: Hot Shots ‘Gameplay Overview’ trailer]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/everybodys-golf-hot-shots-gameplay-overview-trailer</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/everybody%E2%80%99s-golf-hot-shots-%E2%80%98gameplay-overview%E2%80%99-trailer.1227600/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Hit the green.</span>
      </p></div><div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,711 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> and developer <a title="Companies > HYDE [28 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/hyde">HYDE</a> have released a five-minute gameplay overview trailer for <em><a title="Games > Everybody's Golf: Hot Shots [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/everybodys-golf-hot-shots">Everybody’s Golf: Hot Shots</a></em>. <span id="more-975846"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the game, via Bandai Namco:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>Everybody’s favorite golf game series finally returns to the fairway!</p><p>Hit the green with a variety of unique characters and courses in online and offline AND single and multiplayer modes!</p><ul><li>The Classic Gameplay You Love!<!-- AD: content -->
        <ul><li>The controls are as simple and intuitive as ever. Just aim and press the button 3 times at the right moment to master the perfect shot!</li></ul></li><li>Play Solo or With Friends!<ul><li>Climb the ranks in Challenge Mode by completing rounds and facing off against colorful characters.</li><li>Sharpen your skills and focus on beating your personal bests in Solo Rounds.</li><li>Enjoy local <a title="Genres > Multiplayer [532 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/multiplayer">Multiplayer</a> Mode with up to four players on a single controller, or compete online against golfers worldwide.</li><li>For even more excitement, try Wacky Golf—a unique twist on golf that everybody can enjoy together.</li></ul></li></ul><p>Grab your clubs and hit the green with <em>Everybody’s Golf: Hot Shots</em>. Let’s PAR-TEE!</p></blockquote><p><em>Everybody’s Golf: Hot Shots</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,807 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,271 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,577 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2730810/EVERYBODYS_GOLF_HOT_SHOTS/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 4 in Japan and September 5 worldwide.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Gameplay Overview Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="「みんなのGOLF WORLD」ゲーム紹介トレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/quPaomr3XFY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/everybodys-golf-hot-shots-gameplay-overview-trailer]]></content:encoded>
